creditline: Gift of funds from Mary and Bob Mersky
dimension: 29 x 20 in. (73.66 x 50.8 cm) (sheet, as printed)
text: This artwork is part of the series COVID-19: Labor Camp Report. Artist's statement on this artwork originally published on the @laborcamp Instagram account: I am reading more about the long term impacts of COVID-19, and physiological changes of bodies resulting from the disease. I am imagining more metaphysical alterations reflecting a complicated internal space where empathy and doubt, compassion and distrust, hope and fear compete for space.
title: August 17, 2020: Altered by Plague
